```{r pancreas 32330476, include=FALSE}

PMID_32330476 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32330476', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32330476 <- paste0(PMID_32330476$journal,' ', PMID_32330476$year, ' ', PMID_32330476$month,';', PMID_32330476$volume,'(', PMID_32330476$number,'):', PMID_32330476$pages)

PubMed_32330476 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32330476$eprint)

doi_32330476 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32330476$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
